<HEADLINE>
FT  18 SEP 93 / Olympic grants
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BRITAIN'S top Olympic prospects were offered greater financial security
yesterday with the launch of a Pounds 1.3m grant scheme to help with
training and living expenses. The average grant is expected to be Pounds
15,000 a year.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
