FT  18 SEP 93 / UK Company News: Macallan-Glenlivet lower at Pounds 2.16m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Pre-tax profits of Macallan-Glenlivet, the whisky distiller, fell from
Pounds 2.84m to Pounds 2.16m in the half year to the end of June. Turnover
